ker%20developed%20from%20the%20airliner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20filing%20in%20the%20Delaware%20Bankruptcy%20Court%2C%20Astech%20was%20worth%20%2425%20million.%20Boeing%20has%20a%20market%20capitalization%20of%20%24127%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAstech%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%20July%202022%20and%20then%20that%20September%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.bloomberglaw.com%2Fbankruptcy-law%2Fbankrupt-aerospace-firm-astech-wins-approval-to-end-boeing-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminated%20its%20supplier%20contract%20with%20Boeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0sparking%20a%20legal%20contest%20that%20has%20seen%20both%20sides%20accuse%20each%20other%20of%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20after%20the%20contract%20was%20terminated%2C%20Boeing%20brought%20its%20case%20against%20Ten%20Oaks%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20tricked%20into%20approving%20its%20purchase%20of%20Astech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20alleged%20Ten%20Oaks%20said%20it%20would%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20aircraft%20parts%2C%20and%20use%20an%20%2418%20million%20line%20of%20credit%20to%20keep%20Astech%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20assumed%20control%20of%20Astech%2C%20Boeing%20alleges%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bheld%20hostage%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20family%20office%20and%20subject%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bbait%20and%20switch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20Ten%20Oaks%20gave%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bultimatum%26quot%3B%20to%20pay%20three-fold%20more%20for%20the%20parts%2C%20or%20the%20contract%20would%20end%2C%20per%20Boeing's%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ten%20Oaks%20hit%20back%20with%20a%20counterclaim%20last%20Friday%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20duped%20into%20buying%20Astech%20by%20Boeing.%20It%20says%20Boeing's%20claim%20is%20%26quot%3Bexactly%20backward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20Boeing%20that%20benefitted%20as%20a%20result%20of%20that%20purchase%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20Boeing's%20contract%20with%20Astech%20was%20%26quot%3Blopsided%26quot%3B%20and%20leading%20it%20into%20bankruptcy%20because%20the%20pricing%20didn't%20even%20cover%20manufacturing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contract%20was%20agreed%20by%20Astech's%20previous%20owner%2C%20GKN%2C%20in%202012%20and%20was%20set%20to%20last%20until%202028%20with%20prices%20changing%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20Astech%20was%20losing%20%24120%2C000%20on%20each%20exhaust%20kit%20it%20sold%20to%20Boeing%2C%20the%20suit%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20avoid%20losing%20this%20sweetheart%20deal%2C%20Boeing%20fraudulently%20induced%20Counterclaimants%20into%20buying%20that%20supplier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20claimed%20that%20Boeing%20%26quot%3Bhoodwinked%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20office%20into%20%26quot%3Bpurchasing%20the%20assets%20of%20the%20failing%20Astech%20Business%20by%20concealing%20from%20%5BTen%20Oaks%5D%20the%20distressed%20nature%20of%20the%20Astech%20Business%20with%20Boeing%20and%20by%20promising%20financial%20assistance%20that%20it%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20actually%20providing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221098%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20KC-46%20refueling%20via%20hose-and-drogue%20midair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4fb6843bb77284ba4ea7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Boeing%20KC-46%20is%20a%20military%20tanker%20that%20can%20refuel%20fighter%20jets%20in%20midair.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20Oaks%20alleges%20that%20Boeing%20said%20it%20would%20give%20Astech%20financial%20support%20and%20help%20it%20invest%20in%20its%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20accuses%20Boeing%20of%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%26quot%3B%20concealing%20that%20Astech's%20previous%20owner%20threatened%20to%20close%20the%20business%20if%20Boeing%20didn't%20agree%20to%20price%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20was%20already%20looking%20into%20alternative%20suppliers%20in%20case%20Astech%20went%20bankrupt%2C%20the%20complaint%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoeing%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20its%20preposterously%20low-price%20supply%20chain%20for%20many%20months%20longer%20than%20it%20would%20have%20as%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20the%20acquisition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20comes%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20for%20Boeing%2C%20as%20it%20deals%20with%20the%20fall%20out%20from%20January's%20Alaska%20Airlines%20blowout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20preliminary%20report%20released%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20said%20the%20737%20Max%209%20left%20Boeing's%20factory%20without%20key%20bolts%20designed%20to%20secure%20the%20door%20plug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Whitaker%2C%20administrator%20of%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20quality-assurance%20issues%20we%20have%20seen%20are%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-supplier-spirit-aerosystems-scrutiny-over-alaska-blowout-quality-control-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing%20supplier%2C%20Spirit%20AeroSystems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20also%20facing%20scrutiny%20because%20it%20builds%20the%20Max%209%20fuselage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20Oaks'%20lawsuit%20alleges%20Boeing%20has%20suffered%20problems%20with%20suppliers%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20relentless%20drive%20to%20cut%20costs%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20quality%20and%20reliability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-tiny-investment-firm-locked-legal-fight-over-supplier-deal-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%