a%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20We%20demand%20PEN%20take%20significant%20steps%20to%20save%20lives.%20As%20this%20letter%20circulates%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20among%20Palestinian%20writers%20and%20reporters%20will%20likely%20grow.%20On%20October%2025th%20PEN%20International%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20Meanwhile%2C%20PEN%20America%20has%20remained%20silent%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20apparent%20to%20the%20public%20whose%20lives%20and%20voices%20matter%20to%20it%20and%20whose%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20America%20continually%20perpetuates%20fascist%20nation-statehood%2C%20which%20becomes%20especially%20dangerous%20when%20the%20organization%20is%20so%20keen%20to%20define%20literary%20citizenship%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20Whose%20freedom%20does%20PEN%20protect%2C%20if%20outside%20of%20press%20releases%20buried%20on%20its%20website%2C%20PEN%20has%20remained%20silent%20about%20Palestinian%20journalists%2C%20writers%2C%20and%20poets%20murdered%20by%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2031%2C%20PEN%20America%20chose%20to%20platform%20Mayim%20Bialik%2C%20a%20person%20committed%20to%20the%20racist%20ideology%20of%20Zionism.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20PEN%20is%20perpetuating%20dangerous%2C%20fascist%20views%20and%20offering%20tacit%20approval%20for%20the%20Zionist%2C%20racist%20and%20genocidal%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPEN%20Members%20and%20representatives%20from%20Writers%20Against%20the%20War%20On%20Gaza%20(WAWOG)%20protested%20this%20event%20indoors.%20Among%20them%20was%20Randa%20Jarrar%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20writer%20who%20has%20done%20weeks%20of%20unpaid%20labor%20for%20PEN%20as%20an%20event%20host%2C%20organizer%2C%20and%20judge%20of%20PEN%E2%80%99s%20Open%20Book%20prize%20and%20Robert%20Bingham%20prize.%20Rather%20than%20defending%20Jarrar%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20free%20expression%2C%20PEN%20America%20violently%20dragged%20her%20out%20of%20the%20event%20by%20her%20