0select%20their%20AI%20trainer%20through%20Lumin's%20smartphone%20app.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20exercising%20at%20lumin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9057a3d27148878c2fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttendees%20work%20out%20by%20following%20instructions%20from%20the%20AI%20trainer%20through%20their%20headphones.%20%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20trainer%20guides%20gymgoers%20through%20a%20workout%20in%20real%20time%20through%20their%20headphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20algorithms%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20the%20sensors%20count%20an%20exerciser's%20every%20rep%2C%20track%20how%20they%20use%20their%20equipment%2C%20and%20monitor%20their%20movements%20without%20them%20needing%20to%20wear%20a%20piece%20of%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20can%20then%20simultaneously%20analyze%20the%20collected%20data%20and%20give%20exercisers%20real-time%20feedback%20on%20their%20form%2C%20technique%2C%20and%20range%20of%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAttendees%20can%20choose%20between%20a%2040-minute%20solo%20class%20or%20a%20group%20class%20led%20by%20AI.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20lifting%20dumbells%20at%20lumin%20fitness%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9fa6fcb546d2d4d3aa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWomen%20at%20a%20group%20class%20at%20a%20Lumin%20Fitness%20studio.%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESolo%20classes%20generate%20an%20exercise%20plan%20based%20on%20the%20attendee's%20specific%20fitness%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20like%20growing%20certain%20muscle%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroup%20classes%20involve%20a%20high-intensity%20functional%20training%20workout%20designed%20to%20build%20aerob