22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20not%20pictured%2C%20is%20taking%20steps%20to%20ensure%20he%20isn't%20lonely%20when%20he%20enters%20retirement.%3Cp%3Ekeithsutherland%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20hasn't%20retired%20yet%2C%20but%20he%20wants%20to%20ensure%20he%20won't%20be%20lonely%20when%20he%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDescribing%20loneliness%20as%20his%C2%A0%26quot%3Bbiggest%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20plans%20to%20volunteer%20and%20pursue%20hobbies%20upon%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he's%20worried%20that%20older%20adults%20are%20getting%20cast%20to%20the%20side%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20was%20recently%20rewatching%20a%20documentary%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-residents-longevity-secrets-traits-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlue%20Zones%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20led%20him%20to%20rethink%20his%20outlook%20on%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Zones%20are%20regions%20in%20the%20world%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-5-blue-zones-people-live-longest-lives-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhere%20people%20are%20believed%20to%20live%20the%20longest%2C%20healthiest%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20people%20who%20live%20in%20those%20zones%20have%20traits%20that%20include%20living%20with%20purpose%20and%20maintaining%20relationships%20with%20friends%20starting%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20Ed%20%E2%80%94%20who%20requested%20his%20last%20name%20be%20withheld%20for%20privacy%20but%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20said%20there's%20no%20reason%20he%20can't%20incorporate%20those%20ideals%20into%20his%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20people%20were%20actively%20engaged%20in%20their%20community%2C%20they%20were%20doing%20things%2C%20they%20were%20gardening%2C%20they%20were%20actively%20involved%2C%20they%20had%20good%20mobility.%20They%20didn't%20suffer%20any%20of%20the%20degenerative%20ills%20that%20we%20as%20North%20Americans%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Blue%20Zone%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20that's%20part%20and%20parcel%20where%20some%20of%20my%20insight%20comes%20from%2C%20that%20I%20think%20to%20retire%20and%20to%20suddenly%20stop%20and%20to%20say%2C%20'Well%20now%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20nothing%2C'%20is%20going%20to%20kill%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20absolutely%20convinced%20of%20that.%20I%20think%20being%20sedentary%20and%20not%20engaged%20is%20the%20worst%20thing%20that%20you%20can%20put%20upon%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20moving%20from%20Connecticut%20to%20Ontario%2C%20Canada%2C%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20Ed%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20industry%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20sure%20when%20he'll%20officially%20retire.%20But%20he's%20making%20plans%20for%20when%20that%20day%20comes%20to%20avoid%20what%20he%20said%20is%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fnew-surgeon-general-advisory-raises-alarm-about-devastating-impact-epidemic-loneliness-isolation-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bbiggest%20fear%26quot%3B%3A%20being%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20hopes%20that%20upon%20retirement%2C%20he%20can%20pursue%20his%20passion%20for%20bas-relief%20art%2C%20which%20is%20a%20type%20of%20sculpting%20to%20create%20three-dimensional%20figures%20mounted%20on%20two-dimensional%20surfaces%2C%20like%20the%20figures%20on%20certain%20coins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20plans%20to%20volunteer%20at%20nonprofit%20organizations%20and%20shelters%20to%20ensure%20that%20retiring%20from%20his%20job%20doesn't%20also%20mean%20retiring%20from%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20for%20some%20older%20adults%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20that%20easy.%20US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fnew-surgeon-general-advisory-raises-alarm-about-devastating-impact-epidemic-loneliness-isolation-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclared%20loneliness%20an%20epidemic%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alongside%20data%20showing%20poor%20social%20interaction%20could%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20dementia%20among%20older%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20said%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20brighter%20spotlight%20on%20this%20crisis%20because%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20alone%20has%20got%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20are%20suffering%20from%20loneliness%20simply%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20contacts%2C%20their%20children%20aren't%20paying%20attention%20to%20them%2C%20or%20they're%20estranged%20from%20them%20for%20whatever%20reason%20or%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%20being%20alone%20is%20something%20that%20does%20concern%20me.%20And%20I've%20always%20said%20to%20my%20wife%2C%20'Geez%2C%20I%20hope%20I%20go%20before%20you%20do%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20left.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'I%20needed%20to%20do%20something'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20said%20he%20found%20himself%20thinking%20negatively%20about%20his%20retirement%20outlook%20and%20the%20way%20his%20job%20defines%20who%20he%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20loneliness%2C%20his%20thought%20process%20needed%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20to%20think%20of%20myself%20in%20terms%20of%20not%20being%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20working%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20you're%20contributing%2C%20you're%20providing%2C%20and%20suddenly%20that%20stops%2C%20the%20thing%20that%20looms%20in%20the%20distance%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20relevancy%20because%20we%20all%20tend%20to%20identify%20with%20what%20we%20do%20for%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%20in%20terms%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20I'm%20still%20even%20valid%2C%20and%20I%20came%20to%20realize%20these%20are%20not%20good%20thoughts%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ed%20is%20proactively%20planning%20for%20when%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20his%20job%2C%20BI%20has%20previously%20spoken%20to%20some%20older%20adults%20who%20were%20experiencing%20loneliness%20post-retirement%20and%20took%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lamy%2C%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Seattle%2C%20decided%20to%20address%20his%20loneliness%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-crisis-retiree-how-to-achieve-happiness-budget-retirement-seniors-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarting%20a%20group%20at%20his%20senior%20center%20where%20people%20can%20simply%20gather%20and%20chat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20lifesaver%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20similar%20to%20Ed's%20concerns%2C%20leaving%20his%20job%20cut%20%26quot%3Boff%20a%20huge%20flow%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Rick%20Grossman%2C%20a%2070-year-old%20who%20battled%20loneliness%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-villages-loneliness-making-friends-in-retirement-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20a%20solution%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%20village%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20community%20that%20connects%20older%20adults%20in%20the%20same%20region%20to%20resources%20and%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20when%20I%20would've%20just%20stayed%20home%20alone%2C%20and%20now%20I%20will%20do%20some%20of%20the%20things%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20before%2C%20like%20go%20to%20the%20movies%20or%20to%20dinner%2C%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20necessity%20of%20being%20engaged'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20significant%20mental%20and%20physical%20impacts%20of%20experiencing%20loneliness%2C%20Ed%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20issues%26quot%3B%20of%20lacking%20social%20interaction%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20not%20careful%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20my%20life%2C%20my%20life%20expectancy%20will%20diminish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20overall%20well-being%20is%20definitely%20tied%20to%20my%20family%20and%20my%20relationships%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20currency%20is.%20It's%20about%20the%20simple%20act%20and%20the%20necessity%20of%20being%20engaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Murthy's%20efforts%20to%20bring%20awareness%20to%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%2C%20some%20lawmakers%20are%20hoping%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20Congress.%20Democratic%20Sens.%20Chris%20Murphy%20and%20Bob%20Casey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.murphy.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fmurphy-casey-introduce-bill-to-fight-social-isolation-and-loneliness-among-older-americans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20a%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%20%E2%80%94%20called%20Addressing%20Social%20Isolation%20and%20Loneliness%20in%20Older%20Adults%20Act%20%E2%80%94%20to%20establish%20grants%20and%20training%20for%20community-based%20organizations%20to%20help%20address%20loneliness%20in%20older%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20federal%20efforts%20progress%2C%20Ed%20wants%20to%20ensure%20loneliness%20among%20older%20people%20is%20a%20concern%20that%20all%20age%20groups%20work%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20indebtedness%20to%20the%20people%20that%20raised%20us%2C%20the%20generation%20that%20came%20before%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20discard%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that%20what%20we're%20looking%20at%20here%20in%20North%20America%2C%20Canada%20as%20well%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20systemic%20occurrence%20where%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20the%20time.%20And%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3c3327a3d271488789c04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20loneliness%20continues%20to%20hit%20older%20Americans%20particularly%20hard%2C%20Ed%2C%2063%2C%20is%20doing%20everything%20he%20can%20to%20avoid%20that%20outcome%20once%20he%20retires.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mithun%20Chakraborty%20out%20of%20ICU%3B%20feeling%20better%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600891%2Cimgsize-799257.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flatest-health-update-on-mithun-chakraborty-actor-out-of-icu-and-feeling-better%2Farticleshow%2F107600891.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107600891.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMithun%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20veteran%20actor%20and%20politician%2C%20suffered%20an%20Ischemic%20Cerebrovascular%20Stroke%20but%20is%20now%20feeling%20better.%20Known%20for%20films%20like%20'Disco%20Dancer'%20and%20'Mard%2C'%20he%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20is%20currently%20recovering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Ultra-Right%20Party%20Infamous%20For%20Anti-Blasphemy%20Protests%20Slips%20In%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20an%20ultra-right%20Pakistan%20party%20infamous%20for%20sometimes%20bloody%20anti-blasphemy%20agitation%20has%20vowed%20a%20comeback%20after%20its%20vote%20share%20evaporated%20in%20elections%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlasphemy%20is%20a%20charged%20topic%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Pakistan%20where%20the%20faintest%20whisper%20of%20a%20slight%20toward%20the%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20can%20embolden%20lynch%20mobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaad%20Hussain%20Rizvi's%20Tehreek-e-Labbaik%20Pakistan%20(TLP)%20party%20rode%20the%20issue%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20largest%20Islamist%20force%20in%202018%20polls%2C%20but%20its%20prominence%20was%20all%20but%20eroded%20in%20last%20week's%20national%20and%20provincial%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20the%20death%20of%20Rizvi's%20charismatic%20father%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20party%2C%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20patronage%20from%20Pakistan's%20powerful%20generals%20cost%20them%20dearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20supporters%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20cultural%20capital%20Lahore%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Rizvi%20said%20the%20enemies%20of%20Islam%20had%20stopped%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20rigging%20has%20taken%20place%20because%20we%20speak%20about%20rights%2C%20and%20we%20talk%20about%20a%20faith%20that%20those%20with%20power%20in%20this%20world%20do%20not%20accept%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20fill%20his%20father%20Khadim%20Hussain%20Rizvi's%20shoes%2C%20he%20responded%20matter-of-factly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20people%20onto%20the%20streets%2C%20and%20bringing%20people%20out%20to%20vote%20was%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20TLP%20in%20the%20past%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20of%202%2C000%20people%20there%20to%20hear%20him%20speak%20--%20though%20enthusiastic%20--%20was%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20that%20used%20to%20hang%20on%20to%20his%20father's%20every%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhadim%20Rizvi%20had%20the%20kind%20of%20leadership%20and%20charisma%20that%20his%20son%20does%20not%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Arafat%20Mazhar%2C%20who%20works%20on%20blasphemy%20law%20reform%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20religion%20had%20dropped%20down%20the%20pecking%20order%20in%20elections%20defined%20by%20%26quot%3Banti-establishment%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20Pakistan%20battles%20a%20massive%20economic%20crisis%20and%20an%20erosion%20of%20trust%20in%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Have%20God%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETLP%20has%20its%20ideological%20roots%20in%20Barelvi%20Islam%20--%20a%20mainstream%20sect%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20moderate%20but%20for%20which%20blasphemy%20is%20a%20red%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20first%20began%20making%20waves%20in%202016%2C%20when%20protesting%20the%20execution%20of%20Mumtaz%20Qadri%2C%20a%20bodyguard%20who%20assassinated%20the%20governor%20of%20Punjab%20province%20over%20his%20stance%20on%20blasphemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20its%20street%20power%20was%20tapped%20by%20the%20military%20a%20year%20later%20to%20reduce%20the%20voter%20base%20of%20Nawaz%20Sharif's%20centre-right%20party%2C%20which%20had%20fallen%20foul%20of%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20suspicions%20at%20the%20time%20that%20certain%20elements%20within%20intelligence%20agencies%20were%20encouraging%20them%20to%20destabilise%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20public%20policy%20analyst%20Ahmed%20Bilal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20element%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20went%20rogue%20following%20its%20electoral%20success%2C%20orchestrating%20violent%20anti-Sweden%20and%20anti-France%20protests%20after%20incidents%20of%20Koran%20burning%20and%20satirical%20cartoons%20of%20the%20Prophet%20Mohammed%20in%20those%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20on%2C%20Sharif%20is%20back%20in%20favour%20and%20his%20successor%20Imran%20Khan%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20see-saw%20world%20of%20Pakistan%20politics%20--%20reducing%20TLP's%20utility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%20TLP%20bagged%20more%20than%20two%20million%20votes%20to%20become%20the%20fifth-largest%20party%20in%20the%20country%20--%20ahead%20of%20more%20established%20Islamist%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20polls%20were%20less%20successful%20for%20all%20of%20Pakistan's%20religious%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20leading%20Rizvi%20to%20call%20on%20supporters%20to%20come%20out%20and%20protest%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20had%20been%20tipped%20to%20gain%20more%20electoral%20seats%2C%20but%20Mazhar%20said%20its%20appeal%20only%20exists%20in%20times%20of%20perceived%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20not%20an%20imagined%20threat%20around%20the%20prophet%20or%20religion%20in%20the%20country%20then%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20governance%20people%20don't%20want%20them%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20through%20anxiety-inducing%20politics%20that%20they%20can%20get%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizvi%20insists%20they%20will%20be%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20atop%20a%20makeshift%20stage%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%2C%20he%20proclaimed%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20power%2C%20w