ms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107598237.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBipasha%20Basu%20is%20currently%20immersed%20in%20a%20joyful%20chapter%20of%20her%20life%2C%20crafting%20precious%20moments%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover%2C%20and%20their%20beautiful%20daughter%2C%20Devi%20Basu%20Singh%20Grover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2238%20Junior%20Doctors%20Face%20Action%20Over%20Viral%20Reels%20Shot%20In%20Karnataka%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20government%20medical%20college%20in%20Karnataka's%20Gadag%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20junior%20doctors%20recording%20reels%20on%20campus.%20The%20Gadag%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20management%20has%20extended%20housemanship%20--%20meaning%20practical%20training%20--%20of%2038%20junior%20doctors%20by%2010%20days%20after%20reels%20shot%20by%20them%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reels%20showed%20the%20students%20dancing%20in%20their%20scrubs%20in%20the%20hospital%20corridors.%20Another%20showed%20them%20looking%20at%20reports%20and%20holding%20saline%20bottles%20as%20a%20bed%20is%20wheeled%20across.%20After%20the%20reels%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20many%20accused%20the%20junior%20doctors%20of%20neglecting%20their%20duties%20for%20shooting%20quirky%20videos.%20The%20reels%20had%20popular%20Hindi%20and%20Kannada%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20of%20the%20institution%20has%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20mistake%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20students.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20they%20should%20have%20done%20it%20outside%20the%20hospital%20premises%20to%20avoid%20inconvenience%20to%20patients.%20We%20haven't%20granted%20permission%20for%20such%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Basavaraj%20Bommanhalli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20said%20the%20students%20had%20told%20them%20that%20they%20recorded%20the%20reels%20for%20their%20pre-graduation%20ceremony.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20this%2C%20they%20shouldn't%20have%20done%20it.%20Appropriate%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20them.%20Their%20housemanship%20was%20supposed%20to%20end%20in%20the%20next%2010-20%20days%2C%20and%20we%20have%20extended%20that%20by%20another%2010%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReels%20shot%20by%20doctors%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20several%20occasions%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20post-Covid%20era.%20These%20reels%20have%20sharply%20divided%20public%20opinion.%20While%20many%20have%20praised%20doctors%20for%20their%20moves%20and%20seen%20the%20reels%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counter%20work%20stress%2C%20others%20have%20questioned%20if%20such%20conduct%20reflect%20negligence%20towards%20their%20work%20and%20inconvenienced%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707637620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fi40feqo_gadag-institute_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20government%20medical%20college%20in%20Karnataka's%20Gadag%20has%20cracked%20down%20on%20junior%20doctors%20recording%20reels%20on%20campus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-karnataka-college-5036221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgadag-institute-of-medical-sciences-38-junior-doctors-face-action-over-viral-reels-shot-in-k