ual%20economic%20and%20industrial%20policies%2C%20led%20by%20international%20conferences%20and%20agreements%2C%20carbon%20dioxide%20has%20continued%20to%20accumulate%20in%20the%20atmosphere.%20Source%3A%20The%20Conversation%2FCC%20BY%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace-300x284.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace-1024x968.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20rate%20of%20atmospheric%20CO2%20accumulation%20(shown%20in%20parts%20per%20million%20(ppm))%20continues%20to%20accelerate.%20The%20rate%20slowed%20for%20only%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20following%20enactment%20of%20the%20Montreal%20Protocols%2C%20which%20reduced%20the%20use%20of%20chemicals%20known%20to%20threaten%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20atmospheric%20ozone%20layer.%20Image%20credit%3A%20NOAA%2C%20chart%20by%20Barry%20Saxifrage%20at%20NationanalObserver.com%20and%20VisualCarbon.org%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20these%20dismal%20results%2C%20some%20people%20who%20have%20been%20tracking%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20its%20purported%20remedies%20are%20led%20to%20despair.%20Some%20conclude%20that%20human%20beings%20are%20incapable%20of%20living%20without%20destroying%20our%20world.%20But%20this%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20all%20evidence%20from%20the%20course%20of%20human%20evolution.%20People%20just%20like%20us%20have%20been%20around%20for%20nearly%20300%2C000%20years%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20depth%20and%20scale%20of%20global%20environmental%20disruptions%20never%20remotely%20began%20to%20approach%20anything%20like%20we%20face%20now%2C%20until%20perhaps%20ten%20generations%20ago%2C%20less%20than%20three%20hundred%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20changed%3F%20Is%20it%20simply%20human%20greed%2C%20as%20some%20say%3F%20Our%20selfishness%3F%20Apathy%3F%20These%20vices%20have%20certainly%20always%20been%20part%20of%20the%20human%20mix%20and%20no%20doubt%20play%20a%20role%20in%20stymying%20helpful%20responses%20to%20our%20crises.%20But%20why%20did%20it%20take%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20years%20for%20these%20ancient%20traits%20to%20emerge%20as%20fatal%20flaws%3F%20Simplifying%20the%20causes%20of%20our%20complex%20predicament%20to%20a%20few%20of%20the%20worst%20human%20traits%20is%20an%20overly%20narrow%20framing%20of%20the%20problems%20we%20face.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20way%20of%20shifting%20blame%20onto%20a%20small%20coterie%20of%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20the%20heads%20of%20oil%20companies%20or%20political%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20as%20an%20easy%20target%20for%20our%20anger%20or%20unease.%20But%20none%20of%20them%20created%20global%20warming.%20And%20while%20they%20may%20represent%20companies%20or%20groups%20who%20work%20against%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20as%20individuals%20they%20cannot%20stop%20it.%20Their%20actions%20are%20legally%20and%20logistically%20constrained%20by%20the%20same%20systems%20that%20we%20depend%20upon%20for%20our%20modern%20livelihoods%3B%20their%20fossil-fuel%20products%20are%20the%20life-blood%20of%20the%20modern%20economy%20and%20their%20capitalist%20politics%20are%20its%20beating%20heart.%20Those%20CEOs%20and%20politicians%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20merely%20today%E2%80%99s%20winners%20of%20the%20very%20same%20capitalist%20game%20that%20most%20of%20us%20are%20also%20playing%20to%20win%20at%2C%20whenever%20we%20hope%20to%20make%20more%20money%2C%20%E2%80%98get%20ahead%2C%E2%80%99%20or%20promote%20economic%20growth.%20Individual%20blame-mongering%20that%20glosses%20over%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20system%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20most%20of%20us%20earnestly%20vote%20for%20%E2%80%93%20leads%20to%20useless%20or%20even%20dangerous%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221119%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2.png%201119w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2-300x98.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2-1024x336.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696589%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20understand%20that%20how%20we%20frame%20a%20problem%20directs%20where%20we%20look%20for%20answers%2C%20right%20or%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20as%20in%20that%20old%20aphorism%20that%20when%20you%20only%20have%20a%20hammer%2C%20every%20problem%20looks%20like%20a%20nail.%20Or%20the%20apocryphal%20story%20of%20the%20guy%20searching%20for%20his%20keys%20under%20a%20streetlamp%2C%20though%20he%20could%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20them%20anywhere%3B%20%E2%80%98because%20this%20is%20where%20the%20light%20is%20good%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20explains.%20It%20matters%20very%20much%20how%20we%20frame%20the%20predicament%20we%20face%2C%20how%20we%20describe%20its%20causes%20and%20effects%2C%20how%20we%20conceive%20of%20responsibility%20and%20envisage%20justice.%20What%20if%20the%20reason%20our%20response%20to%20global%20warming%20has%20been%20ineffectual%20is%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20asking%20the%20wrong%20questions%3F%20What%20if%20we%E2%80%99re%20framing%20the%20problem%20too%20narrowly%20%E2%80%93%20or%20looking%20entirely%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20one%20example%2C%20consider%20that%20the%20presently%20privileged%20worldview%20describes%20our%20planetary%20system%20primarily%20in%20mechanistic%20terms%20and%20approaches%20every%20difficulty%20as%20a%20set%20of%20engineering%20problems%20to%20be%20optimally%20solved%20for%20furthering%20human%20economic%20growth%20in%20a%20capitalist%2C%20global%2C%20industrial%20economy.%20But%20what%20if%20we%20took%20a%20broader%20view%20grounded%20in%20an%20understanding%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20living%20systems%3F%20The%20discipline%20of%20ecology%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20strives%20toward%20holism%2C%20rather%20than%20mechanism%2C%20in%20understanding%20our%20Earth-system.%20It%20was%20gaining%20prominence%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20but%20then%20quickly%20fell%20out%20of%20fashion%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20dismissed%20by%20many%20as%20too%20%E2%80%98soft%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20science%2C%20which%20might%20well%20be%20translated%20as%20%3Cem%3Enot%20a%20way%20to%20make%20money%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20mainstream%20responses%20to%20climate%20change%20seek%20to%20frame%20the%20problem%20in%20ways%20that%20can%20be%20answered%20by%20%E2%80%98market%20solutions.%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20lens%20through%20which%20our%20institutions%20and%20global%20systems%20have%20learned%20to%20see%20all%20problems.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20sought%20to%20simplify%20and%20reduce%20the%20causes%20and%20consequences%20of%20climate%20change%20to%20technicalities%2C%20whether%20that%E2%80%99s%20temperature%20rise%2C%20sea-level%20rise%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20atmospheric%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20or%20some%20other%20individuated%20metric.%20They%20then%20envision%20technical%20%E2%80%98fixes%E2%80%99%20to%20these%20problems.%20But%20our%20changing%20climate%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20present%20a%20set%20of%20operational%20parameters%20to%20be%20tweaked.%20We%20are%20facing%20a%20fundamental%20revision%20of%20the%20entire%20Earth-system%2C%20a%20dramatic%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20state%20it%20had%20inhabited%20since%20long%20before%20the%20dawn%20of%20human%20civilisation%20toward%20a%20new%20and%20unknown%20state%20for%20the%20future.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20about%20rising%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20but%20a%20degraded%20biosphere%2C%20alterations%20in%20the%20water%20and%20nitrogen%20cycles%2C%20and%20other%20derangements%20%E2%80%93%20in%20fact%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stockholmresilience.org%2F5.3d04209a18a2642b2fc162a3.html%5C%22%3Eexceeded%20six%20of%20the%20nine%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20planetary%20boundaries%20for%20civilizational%20stability.%20And%20we%E2%80%99re%20driving%20these%20destabilising%20changes%20by%20the%20way%20we%20live%2C%20through%20the%20very%20structures%20and%20dynamics%20of%20the%20vaunted%20civilisation%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20preserve.%20Both%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20ecological%20degradation%20caused%20by%20our%20civilisation%20and%20our%20responses%20to%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20future%20of%20all%20life%20on%20Earth%3A%20The%20stakes%20are%20literally%20existential.%20We%20must%20respond%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20effectively%20address%20this%20ecocide%2C%20we%20need%20to%20change%20the%20way%20we%20live%20%E2%80%93%20the%20way%20our%20global%20civilisation%20is%20structured.%20Yet%20billions%20of%20lives%20are%20dependent%20upon%20%3Cem%3Emaintaining%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20present%20systems.%20Drastically%20altering%20patterns%20of%20production%20or%20consumption%20puts%20everybody%20within%20this%20civilisation%20at%20risk.%20This%20makes%20what%20we%20face%20not%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3Eset%20of%20problems%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20a%20%3Cem%3Epredicament.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Problems%20may%20have%20solutions.%20Predicaments%20do%20not.%20Predicaments%2C%20at%20best%2C%20can%20be%20met%20with%20responses%20that%20will%20require%20tradeoffs%2C%20some%20better%20than%20others.%20But%20salutary%20responses%20to%20any%20predicament%20require%20us%20first%20to%20recognise%20our%20situation%20as%20such%2C%20a%20matter%20of%20trade-offs%20resulting%20in%20deep%20systemic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114825%2FS3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221117%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114825%2FS3.png%201117w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114825%2FS3-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114825%2FS3-1024x435.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696590%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20essay%20in%20a%2012-part%20series%20on%20climate%20change.%20In%20this%20series%2C%20I%20intend%20to%20propose%20alternate%20framings%20or%20conceptions%20of%20our%20predicament.%20I%20hope%20first%20to%20break%20out%20beyond%20our%20globally%20dominant%20stories%2C%20to%20broaden%20the%20field%20of%20view%2C%20so%20we%20might%20speak%20about%20things%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20Our%20present%20stories%20%E2%80%93%20like%20those%20that%20reduce%20our%20world%20to%20a%20machine%20with%20discrete%20and%20quantifiable%20parameters%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not%20helping%20us%20to%20formulate%20apt%20and%20adequate%20responses%20to%20our%20ongoing%20crises.%20We%20need%20to%20find%20new%20stories%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20which%20are%20already%20available%20to%20us%20in%20alternate%20conversations%2C%20though%20far%20from%20the%20mainstream%20%E2%80%93%20in%20order%20to%20discover%20better%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20I%20will%20tell%20a%20different%20story%20about%20the%20Earth-system%2C%20how%20our%20planet%20has%20shaped%20us%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20and%20how%20we%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20have%20shaped%20it.%20How%20our%20human%20systems%20are%20merely%20a%20part%20of%20our%20planet%E2%80%99s%20larger%20living%20system%2C%20requiring%20a%20balance%20of%20give-and-take%20for%20us%20to%20thrive.%20And%20what%20has%20recently%20changed%20in%20our%20relationship%20to%20the%20Earth.%20Mindful%20that%20change%20in%20our%20human-systems%20is%20what%E2%80%99s%20now%20required%20%E2%80%93%20finding%20new%20ways%20of%20relating%20to%20each%20other%20and%20our%20planet%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99ll%20also%20consider%20beneficial%20sorts%20of%20responses%20to%20our%20predicament.%20For%20we%20will%20fall%20short%20of%20sensible%20and%20just%20approaches%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20consider%20a%20fuller%20story%20of%20our%20world%2C%20one%20that%20casts%20light%20upon%20ourselves%20as%20living%20parts%20of%20our%20planetary%20system%2C%20considers%20what%20is%20of%20inalienable%20value%20to%20us%2C%20and%20explores%20what%20it%20might%20mean%20for%20humans%20to%20thrive%20within%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20life-sustaining%20bounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUsha%20Alexander%20trained%20in%20science%20and%20anthropology.%20After%20working%20for%20years%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20now%20lives%20in%20Gurugram.%20She%E2%80%99s%20written%20two%20novels%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Legend%20of%20Virinara%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3EOnly%20the%20Eyes%20Are%20Mine%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707636609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113344%2FManali-flood_TheWire-2023.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fearths-changing-climate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We