tion%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaylor-swift-threatens-legal-action-against-student-who-tracks-her-jet-5009356%5C%22%3EJack%20Sweeney%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20student%20who%20tracks%20private%20jets%20of%20celebrities%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBlank%20Space%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehitmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fmusic%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F06%2Ftaylor-swift-jet-cease-desist-jack-sweeney%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Swift's%20lawyers%20have%20sent%20a%20cease-and-desist%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Sweeney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Taylor%20Swift's%20attorney%20accused%20Mr%20Sweeney%20of%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bstalking%20and%20harassing%20behaviours%26quot%3B%20over%20his%20tracking%20of%20the%20American%20singer's%20jet%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20attorney%20Katie%20Wright%20Morrone's%20letter%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20this%20may%20be%20a%20game%20to%20you%2C%20or%20an%20avenue%20that%20you%20hope%20will%20earn%20you%20wealth%20or%20fame%2C%20it%20is%20a%20life-or-death%20matter%20for%20our%20Client.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20added%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20legitimate%20interest%20in%20or%20public%20need%20for%20this%20information%2C%20other%20than%20to%20stalk%2C%20harass%2C%20and%20exert%20dominion%20and%20control%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Jack%20Sweeney%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJack%20Sweeney%20is%20a%20university%20student%20from%20Florida%2C%20United%20States.%20The%2021-year-old%20runs%20several%20social%20media%20accounts%20tracking%20the%20private%20jet%20use%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20other%20celebrities.%20As%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68248168%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Sweeney%20is%20the%20son%20of%20an%20airline%20maintenance%20operations%20controller%20and%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sweeney%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Orlando%2C%20is%20the%20same%20person%20who%20famously%20caught%20Elon%20Musk's%20attention%20for%20tracking%20his%20jet%20travels%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReportedly%2C%20he%20uses%20publicly%20available%20data%20from%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%20and%20broadcasts%20aircraft%20signals%20to%20track%20public%20figures'%20jet%20use%20and%20measure%20their%20carbon%20footprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Taylor%20Swift's%20attorney%20has%20said%20that%20if%20Mr%20Sweeney%20continues%20to%20publish%20information%20tracking%20her%20jet%20travels%2C%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20will%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20pursue%20any%20legal%20remedies%20available%20to%20her%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F06%2Ftech%2Ftaylor-swift-private-jet-tracker%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20letter%20by%20Ms%20Morrone%20accuses%20Mr%20Sweeney%20of%20disregarding%20the%20public%20safety%20of%20others%20%26quot%3Bin%20exchange%20for%20public%20attention%20and%2For%20requests%20for%20financial%20gain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20even%20references%20Elon%20Musk%20offering%20Mr%20Sweeney%20%245%2C000%20to%20delete%20the%20Twitter%20account%20tracking%20his%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%20letter%2C%20the%2021-year-old%20has%20said%20he%20never%20intended%20any%20harm%20with%20his%20actions%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20is%20compiling%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20think%20Swift%20has%20some%20good%20songs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20college%20student%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20transparency%20and%20public%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707633540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.