nt-in-india-report-124021100146_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fisrael-s-tower-semiconductor-proposes-8-bn-chip-plant-in-india-report-124021100146_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fisrael-s-tower-semiconductor-proposes-8-bn-chip-plant-in-india-report-124021100146_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Cops'%20Farmers%20Protest%20Drill%20Leaves%20Residents%20In%20Tears.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20January%2026%2C%202021%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20protesting%20farmers%20clashed%20with%20cops%20on%20the%20capital's%20streets%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20its%20preparations%20to%20stop%20farmers%20from%20entering%20the%20city%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20on%20high%20alert%20ahead%20of%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20the%20national%20capital.%20About%20200%20farmer%20organisations%20are%20part%20of%20the%20protest%20plan.%20They%20have%20several%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20and%20pension%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20capital's%20cops%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20are%20blocking%20the%20city's%20borders%20with%20Haryana%20by%20placing%20massive%20containers.%20Cranes%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20move%20these%20barriers%20if%20farmers%20try%20to%20cross%20into%20Delhi.%20In%20fact%2C%20Haryana%20too%20has%20brought%20in%20cement%20barriers%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20cannot%20enter%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20are%20reportedly%20using%20tractors%20to%20simulate%20the%20protest%20and%20practise%20how%20they%20will%20respond.%20A%20total%20of%2040%20such%20rehearsal%20using%20tractors%20--%2010%20in%20Haryana%2C%2030%20in%20Punjab%20--%20have%20been%20held%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20cops%20are%20holding%20drills%20to%20practise%20firing%20teargas%20shells%20if%20farmers%20refuse%20to%20stop.%20A%20video%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%20shows%20cops%20lining%20up%20and%20firing%20teargas%20shells%20in%20an%20open%20area%20in%20north%20Delhi.%20The%20exercise%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20left%20local%20residents%20in%20discomfort.%20Many%20of%20them%20complained%20of%20burning%20sensation%20in%20their%20eyes%20after%20the%20drill.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20feel%20a%20burning%20sensation%20in%20my%20eye%20and%20nose.%20It%20seems%20my%20eyes%20and%20nose%20have%20got%20blocked%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20local%20resident%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntelligence%20inputs%20say%20as%20many%20as%2020%2C000%20farmers%20with%202%2C000%20tractors%20may%20try%20to%20enter%20Delhi%20day%20after%20tomorrow.%20These%20farmers%20are%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Karnataka.%20The%20cops%20fear%20ant-social%20elements%20can%20enter%20the%20agitation%20and%20disrupt%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20have%20also%20factored%20in%20that%20farmers%20may%20use%20cars%2C%20two-wheelers%2C%20Metro%20or%20buses%20to%20hoodwink%20police.%20Some%20farmers%2C%20they%20said%2C%20may%20also%20come%20beforehand%20and%20gather%20outside%20the%20homes%20of%20VIPs%20such%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20ministers%20and%20BJP%20leaders.%20Women%20and%20children%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20may%20also%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20is%20also%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20social%20media%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20protest.%20The%20foolproof%20preparations%20must%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20shocking%20sights%20on%20Delhi%20roads%20during%20the%202020-21%20farmers'%20agitation%20against%20three%20central%20laws.%20On%20January%2026%2C%202021%2C%20farmers%20had%20entered%20Delhi%20and%20a%20section%20of%20the%20protesters%20had%20turned%20violent.%20Some%20of%20them%20had%20also%20reached%20Red%20Fort%20and%20hoisted%20farmer%20unions'%20flag%20from%20its%20ramparts.%20Hundreds%20were%20injured%20and%20over%2030%20police%20vehicles%20damaged%20as%20farmers%20clashed%20with%20cops.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%2C%20too%2C%20has%20geared%20up%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20at%20Delhi%20borders.%20Cement%20barriers%2C%20barbed%20wires%20and%20sandbags%20are%20in%20place.%20Water%20cannons%20and%20drones%20have%20also%20been%20pressed%20into%20action.%20As%20many%20as%2050%20paramilitary%20companies%20have%20been%20called%20in%20to%20block%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707632700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqgp0jouo_delhi-police-_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-delhi-police-tractor-rehearsals-teargas-drills-delhi-cops-prep-for-farmers-protest-5035807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Determined%20to%20prevent%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20January%2026%2C%202021%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20protesting%20farmers%20clashed%20with%20cops%20on%20the%20capital's%20streets%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20its%20preparations%20to%20stop%20farmers%20from%20entering%20the%20city%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-delhi-police-tractor-rehearsals-teargas-drills-delhi-cops-prep-for-farmers-protest-5035807%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-delhi-police-tractor-rehearsals-teargas-drills-delhi-cops-prep-for-farmers-protest-5035807%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-delhi-police-tractor-rehearsals-tear