termed%20his%20climb%20towards%20number%20one%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BHimalayan%20feat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20show%20stealer%20was%20BoomBall.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20bowled%20extraordinarily.%20He%20is%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20with%2014%20wickets%20and%20also%20the%20number-one-ranked%20Test%20bowler.%20I%20am%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20his%20and%20this%20is%20a%20Himalayan%20feat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spinner%20also%20lauded%20young%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20who%20finally%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20fifty-plus%20score%20after%2012%20Test%20innings%20when%20he%20scored%20a%20century%20in%20the%20second%20Test.%20Ashwin%20said%20that%20Gill's%20talent%20is%20undeniable%20and%20the%20century%20justified%20to%20his%20critics%20the%20armour%20he%20has%20as%20a%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20talent%20that%20Shubman%20Gill%20has.%20But%20the%20hundred%20justified%20just%20the%20kind%20of%20armour%20he%20had%20as%20a%20batter%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20recalled%20that%20the%20match%20was%20evenly%20poised%20on%20day%20four%2C%20but%20the%20team's%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20vibe%2C%20energy%20and%20performance%26quot%3B%20helped%20them%20win.%20The%20veteran%2C%20just%20a%20wicket%20away%20from%20500%20Test%20wickets%2C%20compared%20the%20excitement%20of%20this%20series%20to%20England's%20historic%20Ashes%20series%20at%20home%20against%20Australia%20in%202005%2C%20which%20they%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20into%20the%20fourth%20day%20with%20it%20all%20being%20even-stevens.%20But%20our%20extraordinary%20vibe%2C%20energy%20and%20team%20performance%20helped%20us%20level%20the%20series%201-1.%20England%20played%20an%20exciting%20Ashes%20series%20against%20Australia%20in%202005%20and%20I%20followed%20that%20with%20great%20interest.%20I%20am%20getting%20a%20similar%20feeling%20of%20excitement%