p%3ETrump%20claims%20he%20would%20pass%20that%20-%20maybe%20he%20would%2C%20maybe%20he%20wouldn't%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20mock%20the%20service%20of%20a%20combat%20veteran%2C%20you%20don't%20deserve%20a%20driver's%20license%2C%20let%20alone%20to%20be%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichael%20is%20deployed%20serving%20the%20US%20country%2C%20something%20you%20know%20nothing%20about.%20Someone%20who%20continually%20disrespects%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20military%20families%20has%20no%20business%20being%20commander-in-chief%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20comment%20on%20Haley's%20husband%20also%20drew%20criticism%20from%20various%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20sick%20individual%20would%20put%20down%20a%20service%20member%20who%20is%20deployed.%20This%20disrespects%20every%20military%20family%20in%20our%20country.%20It's%20exactly%20the%20chaos%20we%20don't%20need%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20General%20(rtd)%20Don%20Bolduc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20move%2C%20Michael%20Haley%20fired%20back%20at%20the%20former%20president%2C%20posting%20a%20meme%20on%20Twitter%20reading%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20difference%20between%20humans%20and%20animals%3F%20Animals%20would%20never%20allow%20the%20dumbest%20ones%20to%20lead%20the%20pack%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20mentioning%20Trump's%20account%20in%20the%20caption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20attack%2C%20Trump%20alleged%20that%20Haley%20is%20the%20candidate%20of%20globalists%20and%20warmongers%20who%20want%20to%20spend%20trillions%20and%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20on%20endless%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20radical%20left%20Democrats%20want%20Nikki%20Haley%20because%20they%20know%20that%20she's%20easy%20to%20beat.%20She's%20very%20easy%20to%20beat.%20Haley%20supports%20a%2023%25%20national%20sales%20tax%2C%20and%20she%20wants%20to%20gut%20Medicare%20