%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA065%2Fproduction%2F_132616014_5efbc8e1d76bf6b38ebb124c8e961b8ffd5da7fd0_171_3065_17231000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20presidential%20hopeful%20says%20he%20would%20not%20protect%20any%20country%20failing%20to%20pay%20its%20bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2026%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Politics%20Bounces%20Back%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dust%20settles%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20recently%20concluded%20elections%2C%20some%20underlying%20facts%20will%20come%20into%20clearer%20focus%2C%20namely%20the%20further%20entrenchment%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20first%20the%20dust.%20The%20resilience%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaaf%20(PTI)%20is%2C%20obviously%20enough%2C%20the%20big%20story.%20After%20he%20had%20fallen%20out%20with%20his%20former%20mentors%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20euphemism%20for%20the%20armed%20forces%E2%80%99%20extra-constitutional%20political%20power%20%E2%80%93%20he%20ended%20up%20in%20detention%2C%20and%20his%20party%20was%20put%20under%20legal%20and%20extra-legal%20pressures.%20In%20what%20became%20a%20test%20of%20their%20organisational%20ability%2C%20the%20party%20was%20unable%20to%20retain%20a%20unified%20election%20symbol%20and%20its%20nominees%20were%20forced%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20as%20independent%20candidates.%20Despite%20these%20disadvantages%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20absence%20from%20the%20campaign%20of%20its%20popular%20leader%2C%20PTI%20managed%20to%20win%20more%20seats%20than%20any%20other%20party%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20got%20a%20landslide%20majority%20in%20the%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20It%20also%20went%20neck%20and%20neck%20with%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20in%20the%20most%20populous%20Punjab%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20supporters%20who%20are%20prone%20to%20grandiose%20historical%20comparisons%20are%20incorrect%20in%20claiming%20that%20either%20their%20persecution%20or%20their%20performance%20was%20unprecedented.%20Claims%20of%20bias%20are%20valid%20but%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20egregious%20deviations%20from%20past%20practice.%20The%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20Musharraf%20regime%20and%20its%20alleged%20collaborators%20before%20the%202008%20elections%20against%20its%20opponents%20claimed%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20including%20that%20of%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20In%20the%202013%20elections%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%20selectively%20threatened%20and%20then%20attacked%20campaigns%20of%20three%20parties%20(PPP%2C%20ANP%20and%20MQM)%2C%20murdering%20party%20supporters%20and%20kidnapping%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Yusuf%20Raza%20Gillani%20from%20a%20campaign%20event.%20The%20persecution%20of%20PMLN%20leaders%20and%20candidates%20in%202018%20was%2C%20arguably%2C%20no%20less%20severe%20than%20what%20PTI%20faced%20this%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20defiance%20and%20%E2%80%98bounce%E2%80%99%20are%20also%20not%20unprecedented.%20The%20PPP%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20went%20on%20to%20fight%20and%20win%20the%202008%20elections%20on%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%20is%20the%20best%20revenge%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20PMLN%20made%20a%20good%20showing%20in%202018%20on%20the%20chant%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evote%20ko%20izzat%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20vote%E2%80%9D.%20PTI%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20other%20parties%20when%20it%20too%20turned%20to%20the%20ballot%20as%20its%20primary%20form%20of%20protest%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ezulm%20ka%20badla%3C%2Fem%3E%20vote%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20to%20avenge%20injustice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20comes%20next%20is%20complicated%20for%20both%20the%20PTI%20and%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%20would%20want%20to%20use%20the%20electoral%20resilience%20of%20his%20party%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20establishment%20for%20his%20way%20out%20of%20detention%20and%20court%20cases%2C%20and%20possibly%20back%20into%20office.%20But%20while%20the%20political%20wind%20might%20be%20with%20him%2C%20parliamentary%20arithmetic%20is%20not.%20According%20to%20results%20already%20published%20by%20the%20election%20commission%2C%20PTI%20supported%20independents%20would%20constitute%20the%20largest%20bloc%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%20but%20fall%20well%20short%20of%20an%20overall%20majority.%20PTI%20leaders%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20been%20cheated%20out%20of%20many%20seats%20and%20that%20if%20awarded%20they%20would%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20national%20and%20Punjab%20assemblies.%20Some%2C%20though%20not%20all%2C%20such%20claims%20might%20be%20valid%2C%20but%20legal%20challenges%20to%20declared%20results%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20long%20drawn%20affairs%20with%20no%20guarantee%20of%20success.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%20parliamentary%20business%20will%20need%20to%20be%20attended%20to%2C%20and%20PMLN%20with%20somewhat%20fewer%20seats%20than%20PTI%2C%20but%20with%20ongoing%20relationships%20with%20other%20parties%20and%20non-PTI%20independents%2C%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20use%20the%20momentum%20of%20its%20election%20win%20to%20switch%20to%20protest%20mode%E2%80%93%20about%20election%20irregularities%20and%20then%20about%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20detention.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20fondness%20and%20ability%20to%20elevate%20his%20own%20person%20to%20a%20point%20of%20principle%20means%20that%20he%20might%20well%20demand%20this%20of%20his%20followers.%C2%A0%20One%20example%20of%20such%20audacity%20was%20the%20failed%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20on%20May%209%2C%202023%20when%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20staged%20violent%20attacks%20on%20state%20symbols%20and%20military%20facilities%20in%20protest%20against%20his%20detention%20in%20a%20court%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Have%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-have-the-pakistan-elections-made-the-countrys-crisis-worse%5C%22%3EHave%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20PTI%20winning%20candidates%20might%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20humdrum%20processes%20of%20parliamentary%20politics%2C%20while%20keeping%20up%20lip%20service%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20their%20detained%20leader.%20They%20have%20an%20incontrovertible%20claim%20to%20forming%20the%20provincial%20government%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20and%20would%20constitute%20a%20powerful%20opposition%20in%20Punjab%20and%20in%20Islamabad.%20Getting%20involved%20in%20parliamentary%20politics%20and%20in%20returning%20to%20office%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20would%20involve%20some%20level%20of%20autonomy%20from%20the%20whims%20of%20their%20popular%20leader.%20And%20it%20may%20expose%20them%20to%20fissures%20and%20factionalism.%20This%20process%20will%20start%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20few%20days%20from%20now%20when%20the%20PTI%20group%20will%20have%20to%20agree%20on%20parliamentary%20tactics%20and%20leadership%20positions%20nationally%20and%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20government%20formation%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conundrum%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20is%20no%20less%20complicated.%20The%20PTI%20was%20mentored%20into%20office%20in%202018%20to%20disrupt%20political%20accommodation%20between%20the%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20encroaching%20upon%20the%20extra-constitutional%20powers%20of%20the%20establishment.%20Successive%20constitutional%20and%20legislative%20changes%20particularly%20the%2018th%20Constitutional%20Amendment%2C%20the%20completion%20of%20parliamentary%20terms%2C%20and%20rival%20parties%20leading%20the%20various%20provincial%20and%20federal%20governments%20were%20all%20indicators%20of%20the%20consolidation%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20The%20PTI%20echoed%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20distaste%20for%20political%20accommodation%2C%20and%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20magnified%20the%20narrative%20that%20politics%20and%20professional%20politicians%20are%20all%20about%20self-serving%20deal-making.%20He%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20this%20system%20and%20to%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20more%20unitarian%20model%20with%20himself%20at%20the%20helm%20ably%20assisted%20by%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20political%20ambitions%20brought%20him%20into%20conflict%20with%20his%20erstwhile%20mentors%20whose%20designated%20role%20for%20him%20was%20to%20disrupt%20the%20PMLN-PPP%20compact%20but%20who%20had%20not%20thought%20things%20through%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20establishment%20needs%20to%20hold%20Khan%20down%20because%20he%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20an%20unreliable%20interlocutor.%20It%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20accept%20broader%20accommodation%20between%20the%20other%20political%20parties.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20remarkable%20but%20unnoticed%20feature%20of%20the%20election%20results%20is%20the%20continuity%20in%20the%20popular%20mandate.%20The%20number%20of%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20main%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20PTI%2C%20PMLN%2C%20PPP%20%E2%80%93%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20outcome%20in%202018.%20And%20as%20in%202018%2C%20the%20PTI%20has%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh%2C%20while%20Punjab%20remains%20split%20down%20the%20middle.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%202024%20elections%20represent%20the%20third%20successive%20PTI%20win%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20and%20the%20fourth%20one%20for%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh.%20Party%20positions%20in%20national%20assembly%20seats%20from%20the%20provinces%20correspond%20closely%20with%20provincial%20assembly%20outcomes.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20leader%20has%20not%20dented%20the%20silent%20but%20steady%20shift%20of%20the%20centre%20of%20political%20gravity%20from%20Islamabad%20to%20the%20provincial%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20results%20demonstrated%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20resilience%20of%20his%20party.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20change%20other%20salient%20facts.%20The%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20at%20cornering%20politicians%20through%20the%20anti-politics%20Khan%20was%20hoisted%20on%20its%20own%20petard.%20The%20failure%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20attempted%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20of%20May%202023%20still%20looms%20heavy%20and%20there%20will%20be%20little%20appetite%20among%20his%20supporters%20or%20the%20public%20at%20large%20for%20the%20renewal%20of%20street%20protests%20in%20Punjab.%20In%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20the%20PTI%20will%20have%20little%20reason%20to%20protest%2C%20as%20it%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20sending%20its%20legislators%20and%20their%20supporters%20scrambling%20for%20office%20and%20favour.%20The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%20Elected%20politicians%2C%20in%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20their%20work%20cut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHaris%20Gazdar%20is%20Senior%20Researcher%2C%20Collective%20for%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20Karachi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trinidad%20and%20Tobago%20hit%20by%20mystery%20ship%20oil%20spill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707626311000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F65CD%2Fproduction%2F_132616062_gettyimages-1993696559.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68266339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2015km%20(nine%20miles)%20of%20Tobago's%20coast%20is%20already%20affected%20after%20a%20mysterious%20ship%20overturned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68266339%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68266339.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68266339.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20a%20Storyteller%3A%20An%20Interview%20With%20'Quarterlife'%20Author%20Devika%20Rege%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11094350%2FProfile-for-the-Wire.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKozhikode%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDevika%20Rege%E2%80%99s%20debut%20novel%20%3Cem%3EQuarterlife%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20an%20exploration%20into%20the%20minds%20and%20lives%20of%20young%20India%20in%20the%20years%20around%202014%20%E2%80%93%20a%20time%20which%20saw%20political%20shifts%20the%20country%2C%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20still%20living%20under.%20Starting%20with%20with%20the%20narratives%20of%20three%20protagonists%2C%20each%20experiencing%20and%20living%20the%20shifts%20differently%2C%20the%20novel%20then%20expands%20to%20create%20a%20multi-character%20narrative%20that%20feels%20like%20an%20expansive%20journey%20into%20the%20protagonists%E2%80%99%20lives%20and%20minds%2C%20approaching%20all%20the%20different%20stories%20with%20a%20familiarity%20and%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20novel%20opens%20with%20Naren%20Agashe%2C%20who%20decides%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India%20after%20working%20at%20a%20multinational%20in%20the%20US%20because%20of%20the%20economic%20opportunities%20he%20believes%20are%20opening%20up%2C%20and%20because%20an%20isolated%20life%20in%20the%20States%20was%20making%20him%20unhappy.%20He%20is%20joined%20on%20his%20journey%20home%20by%20Amanda%2C%20a%20college%20classmate%20who%20wants%20to%20volunteer%20in%20India.%20Naren%E2%80%99s%20younger%20brother%2C%20Rohit%2C%20is%20an%20aspiring%20film%20producer%20with%20boyish%20charms%20who%20is%20looking%20for%20his%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20isn%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20the%20three%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20it%20grows%20to%20encompass%20their%20friends%2C%20families%20and%20the%20people%20they%20encounter%2C%20including%20Omkar%20Khaire%2C%20a%20filmmaker%20and%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekaryakarta%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERege%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20choices%20she%20made%20in%20her%20book%2C%20how%20its%20central%20theme%20emerged%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20book%20is%20set%20in%20a%20very%20precise%20moment%2C%20right%20after%20the%202014%20elections.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20moment%20I%20think%20everyone%20would%20agree%20was%20pivotal%2C%20though%20they%20may%20have%20different%20opinions%20on%20it.%20And%20that%20moment%20still%20feels%20exceedingly%20present%2C%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20still%20feeling%20the%20impact%20of%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20continuing.%20What%20drew%20you%20to%20this%20as%20the%20setting%20for%20your%20book%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moment%20might%20be%20precise%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20the%20novel%20feels%20relevant%20to%20a%20much%20longer%20arc.%202014%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20widescale%20moral%2C%20cultural%20and%20economic%20changes%20in%20Indian%20society%20that%20had%20been%20afoot%20since%20the%20nineties%2C%20if%20not%20before.%20There%20was%20also%20much%20in%20the%20air%20that%20had%20echoes%20with%20other%20democracies%2C%20like%20the%20rise%20of%20conservative%20forces%2C%20the%20fallouts%20of%20late%20stage%20capitalism%2C%20and%20a%20fatigue%20with%20liberal%20ideals.%20As%20a%20writer%2C%20I%20had%20been%20feeling%20into%20these%20anxieties%20with%20my%20early%20work%2C%20and%20the%20election%20clarified%20how%20they%20were%20connected.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20overemphasis%20on%20the%20novel%E2%80%99s%20setting%20often%20makes%20me%20uncomfortable.%20The%20moment%20was%20merely%20a%20frame%20through%20which%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20something%20deeper%E2%80%A6like%20the%20psychology%20underlying%20our%20political%20or%20economic%20beliefs%20and%20how%20these%20are%20mediated%20by%20our%20conscience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20270px)%2085vw%2C%20270px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11100613%2FQuarterlife_FC-768x1215-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11100613%2FQuarterlife_FC-768x1215-1.jpeg%20759w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11100613%2FQuarterlife_FC-768x1215-1-190x300.jpeg%20190w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11100613%2FQuarterlife_FC-768x1215-1-648x1024.jpeg%20648w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDevika%20Rege%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EQuarterlife%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20does%20the%20novel%20open%20with%20the%20perspectives%20of%20Rohit%2C%20Amanda%20and%20Naren%3F%20I%20was%20especially%20curious%20about%20Amanda%20as%20an%20American%20in%20a%20story%20set%20in%20India.%20What%20is%20her%20relevance%20to%20the%20novel%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20character%20was%20an%20occasion%20to%20explore%20a%20certain%20worldview%20and%20dimension%20of%20the%20times.%20At%20the%20start%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Amanda%20and%20Naren%20also%20offered%20a%20useful%20triumvirate%20of%20perspectives%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20insider%2C%20the%20outsider%2C%20and%20the%20insider-outsider.%20That%20Amanda%20is%20an%20American%20with%20English%20ancestors%20is%20not%20irrelevant%20because%20the%20dynamic%20between%20East%20and%20West%20has%20shaped%20our%20identity%20for%20centuries.%20Since%20liberalisation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20more%20taken%20up%20with%20the%20US%20than%20the%20UK.%20A%20lot%20of%20middle-class%20kids%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9990s%20grew%20up%20on%20American%20movies%20and%20music.%20The%20brain%20drain%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20was%20at%20its%20peak.%20Wealthy%20cousins%20who%20went%20to%20the%20States%20for%20a%20summer%20came%20back%20with%20an%20accent.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20admit%20that%20now.%20There%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20cultural%20shift%2C%20and%20we%20are%20desperate%20to%20destroy%20the%20white%20gaze%20with%20an%20urgency%20that%20both%20Naren%20and%20Rohit%20suffer.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20person%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20What%20happens%20when%20they%20are%20dehumanised%3F%20Does%20it%20liberate%20us%3F%20To%20explore%20such%20questions%2C%20Amanda%20had%20to%20have%20a%20full%20life.%20It%20also%20felt%20important%20that%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20an%20instrument%20for%20the%20Indians%20to%20know%20themselves%20better.%20The%20novel%20may%20be%20set%20largely%20in%20India%2C%20but%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20about%20India%20alone.%20If%20it%20was%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20simpler%20novel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20in%20the%20book%20where%20all%20the%20characters%20start%20arguing%20about%20politics.%20Fault%20lines%20that%20were%20already%20starting%20to%20show%20come%20out%20starkly%2C%20and%20the%20argument%20ends%20badly.%20Would%20that%20conversation%20have%20looked%20different%20today%3F%20Would%20it%20have%20happened%20at%20all%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20more%20such%20conversations%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20think.%20Whether%20it%20was%202014%20in%20India%20or%202016%20in%20the%20US%20or%20Brexit%2C%20several%20democracies%20were%20witnessing%20a%20period%20of%20acute%20polarisation%20at%20the%20level%20of%20friends%20and%20family.%20Suddenly%2C%20whom%20a%20person%20voted%20for%20seemed%20to%20betray%20something%20essential%20about%20their%20character.%20Whether%20or%20not%20this%20is%20true%2C%20those%20of%20us%20who%20came%20of%20age%20then%20will%20remember%20how%20such%20inflection%20points%20made%20us%20aware%20of%20the%20differences%20among%20our%20closest.%20Now%20the%20filters%20come%20on%20earlier.%20A%20college%20student%20recently%20told%20me%20that%20unlike%20the%20characters%20in%20%3Cem%3EQuarterlife%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20would%20not%20make%20friends%20who%20hold%20such%20different%20views%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20There%20are%20subjects%20that%20families%20have%20banned%20at%20dinner%20and%20on%20groups%20online.%20Dialogue%20has%20entirely%20broken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EYour%20book%20delves%20into%20the%20interiority%20of%20all%20its%20characters%2C%20often%20telling%20us%20what%20is%20happening%20externally%20through%20their%20perspective.%20What%20drew%20you%20to%20this%20exploration%20of%20interiority%20as%20a%20feature%20of%20the%20narrative%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20choice%20was%20instinctive%20at%20first.%20It%20may%20have%20had%20to%20do%20with%20what%20I%20find%20interesting%20about%20people%20or%20the%20form%2C%20since%20no%20medium%20allows%20you%20to%20inhabit%20the%20minute-to-minute%20thoughts%20of%20multiple%20characters%20in%20language%20quite%20like%20the%20novel.%20But%20as%20I%20kept%20at%20it%2C%20I%20also%20found%20the%20technique%20especially%20relevant%20to%20what%20I%20was%20attempting%20with%20this%20particular%20book.%20It%20pushed%20me%20past%20my%20own%20assumptions%20about%20people%20by%20forcing%20me%20to%20understand%20them%20more%20fully%20than%20if%20I%20had%20written%20them%20only%20from%20the%20outside.%20It%20also%20raised%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20representation%2C%20the%20tension%20between%20empathy%20and%20judgment%2C%20and%20between%20ethics%20and%20aesthetics%2C%20many%20of%20which%20felt%20relevant%20not%20just%20to%20art%20but%20to%20our%20responsibilities%20and%20moral%20dilemmas%20as%20everyday%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20voice%20changes%20a%20little%20with%20each%20character%E2%80%99s%20perspective.%20In%20places%2C%20Amanda%E2%80%99s%20voice%20comes%20in%20anecdotes%2C%20almost%20like%20diary%20entries%2C%20while%20Naren%E2%80%99s%20feels%20more%20like%20an%20interior%20monologue.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20change%20of%20literary%20form%20and%20the%20number%20of%20voices%20with%20each%20section.%20Did%20that%20come%20naturally%20as%20well%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20grew%20organically%20in%20that%20each%20movement%20was%20a%20response%20to%20the%20last.%20To%20state%20the%20rationale%20for%20every%20gesture%20would%20flatten%20the%20reading%20experience%2C%20but%20I%20can%20share%20something%20my%20editor%20said%20the%20other%20day.%20She%20described%20%3Cem%3EQuarterlife%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20novel%20that%20endlessly%20mushrooms%20outwards.%20Most%20novels%20introduce%20a%20set%20of%20characters%20in%20the%20first%20half%20and%20resolve%20their%20arcs%20in%20the%20second%2C%20but%20in%20%3Cem%3EQuarterlife%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20new%20characters%20keep%20appearing%20in%20even%20the%20final%20chapters%20and%20reference%20still%20others%20beyond.%20Some%20readers%20have%20found%20this%20exasperating.%20I%20suppose%20it%20defies%20the%20usual%20tenets%20of%20storytelling%2C%20but%20frankly%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20as%20a%20storyteller.%20Everyone%20is%20peddling%20stories%20these%20days%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20celebrities%2C%20politicians%20or%20brands%2C%20and%20there%20is%20something%20violent%20about%20a%20too-tidy%20narrative%20of%20human%20consciousness%20or%20history.%20As%20I%20understand%20it%2C%20the%20novelist%E2%80%99s%20task%20is%20to%20make%20meaning%20of%20the%20ideas%20of%20an%20epoch%20through%20a%20textual%20form%20that%20is%20uniquely%20spacious%20and%20versatile.%20To%20think%20of%20fiction%20as%20anything%20less%20is%20to%20underestimate%20its%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707626243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11094350%2FProfile-for-the-Wire.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fnot-a-storyteller-an-interview-with-quarte