ate%20exotic%20mushrooms%20in%2010%20days.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20co-founders%20Prithvi%20Kini%20(30)%20and%20Jashid%20Hameed%20(32)%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20DIY%20kits%20and%20their%20obsession%20with%20mushrooms%20that%20took%20them%20to%20Shark%20Tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20shared%20fondness%20for%20mushrooms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20after%20completing%20her%20higher%20studies%20in%20philosophy%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Shri%20Ram%20College%20For%20Women%2C%20Prithvi%20worked%20with%20Bengaluru-based%20startups%20focusing%20on%20science%20and%20technology.%20Whereas%20Jashid%20graduated%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%20and%20then%20pursued%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20from%20IIM%20Indore%20in%202017.%20He%20worked%20with%20Aditya%20Birla%20Fashion%20and%20Retail%20Ltd%20as%20area%20operations%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20their%20lives%20when%20they%20met%20each%20other%20on%20an%20online%20dating%20application.%20As%20their%20love%20story%20evolved%2C%20they%20discovered%20their%20life%20goals%20in%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20that%20the%20couple%20discovered%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329202%2Fgwalior-professor-nidhi-katare-becomes-successful-mushroom-farmer-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20of%20mushroom%3C%2Fa%3E-based%20extracts%20and%20started%20sourcing%20wellness%20products%20from%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMushrooms%20essentially%20help%20in%20stress%20relief%2C%20mental%20well-being%2C%20gut%20health%2C%20anxiety%2C%20cardiovascular%20health%2C%20and%20athletic%20performance.%20After%20experiencing%20their%20health%20benefits%2C%20we%20started%20looking%20for%20alternatives%20or%20Indian%20brands%2