ie%20who%20has%20launched%20raptorX.ai%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20firm%20that%20is%20helping%20businesses%20combat%20cyber%20malware%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Pratyusha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%2C%20if%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20phishing%20practices%2C%20how%20are%20so%20many%20still%20being%20scammed%3F%20Why%20has%20the%20recent%20past%20seen%20an%20erosion%20of%20trust%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199904%2Fmumbai-startup-tb-artificial-intelligence-innovation-tuberculosis-diagnosis-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20transactions%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20tend%20to%20overlook%20the%20finer%20nuances%2C%E2%80%9D%20answers%20Pratyusha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20message%20has%20a%20source.%20I%E2%80%99d%20suggest%20looking%20at%20the%20source%20and%20the%20details%20of%20the%20message%20clearly.%20If%20it%20is%20a%20website%2C%20along%20with%20ensuring%20the%20site%20is%20secure%2C%20also%20check%20the%20contact%20information%20provided.%20Try%20getting%20in%20touch%20with%20them%20to%20check%20the%20legitimacy%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20their%20policies.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20juggling%20all%20of%20this%20while%20shopping%20online%20is%20a%20task%2C%20agrees%20the%20techie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20big%20list%20of%20things%2C%20but%20since%20we%20are%20all%20strapped%20for%20time%2C%20AI%20can%20be%20used%20to%20run%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334480%2Ffem-tech-startup-for-women-mind-and-mom-by-padmini-janaki-pregnancy-ivf-consultation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20algorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20predict%20the%20fraudulent%20nature%20of%20websites%20or%20SMSes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd